HEADWORD: palpate
<hw>palpate</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To examine for medical purposes
by touching, as of body parts; <as>as, the nurse <ex>palpated</ex> the
patient's stomach</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> feel.</syn>⟦br⟧
